# Drop Grafana dashboard JSON files in this folder. They will be auto-loaded
# every 30s via the provider defined in ../provisioning/dashboards/dashboards.yml.
#
# Recommended starters (download JSON from grafana.com/grafana/dashboards):
#   - Node Exporter Full       ID 1860   -> node-exporter-full.json
#   - Docker / cAdvisor compute  ID 14282 -> cadvisor.json
#   - Prometheus 2.0 Overview  ID 3662   -> prometheus.json
